  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Empower Ixil Guatemalan children through education</narrative>
  </title>
  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">The Centro provides educational opportunities to indigenous children+youth in the rural community of La Pista (pop~3,000) and surrounding communities.  We supplement the rudimentary local school learning opportunities with free classes for children, computer and internet literacy courses, arts and skills development.  In 2016, 1,734 children/youth were supported by the centre and 17,520 nutritious meals were served. Through Feb 2018 we commemorate the fervent support of beloved Philip Van Kirk.</narrative>
  </description>
